All Implemented Interfaces:
DecorativeWriter, Writer
public class TrimWriter
extends AbstractDecorativeWriter

Trims text as it is written. It has a normal and a multiline mode. In the normal mode, the text that's written is being trimmed in its entirety. In multiline mode, each line is being trimmed individually.
